summary: Fixes problem when u can`t your name with compound words (names contain spaces)
descriptionHtml:
This is file for those who have problem with compound names in item enchant menu. People who are playing english version game won`t need it, but on Polish version nameing item does not work correctly (Fixes problem with names, eg. Sword of God won`t work, u must use SwordOfGod now is fully fixed) May also work on other language game version.

Installation:
Put bottombar.swf from archive to data/interface/inventory components
author: psychodracon
